<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    
    <hr>
    
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "jvaz_about_pic.jpeg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-image' %>
        
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div 
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>  
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>We are Julia A. Valentine and Tabitha Valentine Morales, a Coldwell Banker Residential Realty team 
        located in choice Fountain Hills, AZ (#fabfountainhills).</p>  
        
        <p>After years of living abroad, including Europe, Australia, Costa Rica and Panama, we made Arizona our home in 2005.  
        We know  why Phoenix was voted the 2015 # 1 retirement location in America ! 
        "Good weather and a high well-being score" is just part of the story. 
        Come see why people of all ages find the Arizona lifestyle irresistible!</p>
        
        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#locationExpertise"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="locationExpertise"
          >
            Location Expertise 
          </button>
          
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#reviews"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="reviews"
          >
            Reviews
          </button>
        </p>
        
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="locationExpertise">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Phoenix
            </div>
             <div class="card card-block">
              Biltmore
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="collapse" id="reviews">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Reviews 1
            </div>
             <div class="card card-block">
              Reviews 2
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>



